Title: Moose on the Loose
Writer: Johnny J. Sullivan (story), Johnny J. Sullivan
Actors: Johnny J. Sullivan, Mandy Schneider, Reasha Honaker, Jody Mortara
Plot: After an adventure in Canada, a filmmaker returns to Los Angeles and comes to realize the journey is far from over. He struggles to learn how to embrace the adventure - one that has been wildly audacious, revealing and informative.
